This paper deals with data integration and entity consolidation, which are common problems in database management. Therefore, cs.DB (Databases) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also mentions truth discovery and data fusion methods, which are commonly used in information retrieval (cs.IR) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The proposed method uses unsupervised learning, which falls under the umbrella of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG).
